<h4 id="tabä¸ç©ºæ ¼æ›¿æ¢">tabä¸ç©ºæ ¼æ›¿æ¢</h4>
<p>a tab could be a different number of columns depending on your enviroment</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code># substitue tab for space
:set ts=4
:set expandtab
:%retab!

# substitue space for tab
:set ts=4
:set noexpandtab
:%retab!
</code></pre></div></div>

